[DOCUMENT]
TITLE: Bridge requirements

OPTIONS:
  MARKUP: Markdown

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: BR-001
TITLE: Connection setup
STATEMENT: >>>
The bridge **must** establish a connection within 5 seconds of startup.

A retry policy is **out of scope** for this requirement.
<<<

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: BR-002
TITLE: Heartbeat
STATEMENT: The bridge MUST emit a heartbeat every 1000 milliseconds.

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: BR-003
TITLE: Reconnect
STATEMENT: The bridge MUST attempt reconnection on link loss.
